{"tid":2295384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"又係「豁免檢疫」致爆發？尼泊爾駐港領事館職員豁免檢疫入境，申報無病徵，確診後醒悟之前曾出現病徵","createTime":"2020-11-21T17:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T17:52:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64af1ae60e73189e7080c65750d0691817c45a84","tid":2295384,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T17:50:04.000Z","msg":"尼泊爾駐港領事館今日表示，一名職員確診新冠肺炎，領事館今日起停止服務直至另行通知，職員將在家工作繼續處理緊急事務。<br />\n<br />\n  本港一名昨日確診30歲女子，是尼泊爾抵港的免檢疫者，抵港前已出現病徵，抵港後曾住紅磡都會軒1座。衛生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君解釋，她填寫健康申報表時不認為自己有病徵，因而沒有申報，但在確診後，中心再向她核實，她才醒悟之前曾出現病徵。張竹君說，以衛生角度而言，入境措施雖然越緊越好，但也要考慮實際運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/localnews/30歲女職員確診-尼泊爾駐港領事館即日起停止服務\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Flocalnews%2F30%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%B0%BC%E6%B3%8A%E7%88%BE%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E9%A4%A8%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r5ktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=5a4b7599\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/localnews/30歲女職員確診-尼泊爾駐港領事館即日起停止服務</a>"},{"pid":"f664cc99583fb7747c16124d35f5cf601ba4ab3c","tid":2295384,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T17:51:07.000Z","msg":"你肯定？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C38h1yj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC38h1yj.png&h=cd60f871&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de3d85293a41596c913ba56d222283870019a733","tid":2295384,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T17:51:14.000Z","msg":"自尼泊爾及印度的輸入個案帶有<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">全新</span></span></strong>的GH型病毒株 ！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" 